description: Navigate to Onoe-cho. Start at the Onoe-cho intersection, facing the wide tree-lined avenue with the List Sotheby's building on the left and the Konaka building on the right. Proceed straight through the intersection, keeping the List Sotheby's building on your left. Continue straight along the main road for about 80 meters; the destination will be on the right side near the Maibasuketto (AEON) store.
agent_refined_route: Head straight through Onoe-cho intersection -> Continue straight on the main road [79m]
